WEBVTT

00:00:00.933 --> 00:00:03.607
2014. je stvarno jako posebna godina
za mene:

00:00:03.737 --> 00:00:05.614
20 godina kao konzultant,

00:00:05.614 --> 00:00:07.436
20 godina braka,

00:00:07.436 --> 00:00:10.387
i slaviti ću 50 godina kroz jedan mjesec.

00:00:10.887 --> 00:00:15.837
To znači da sam rođen 1964.
u malom gradu u Njemačkoj.

00:00:16.437 --> 00:00:18.155
Bio je to sivi dan u studenom,

00:00:18.155 --> 00:00:19.575
a ja sam zakasnio.

00:00:20.035 --> 00:00:23.518
Osoblje rodilišta 
je zaista bilo preopterećeno

00:00:23.518 --> 00:00:27.443
jer se jako puno beba rodilo tog
sivog dana u studenom.

00:00:28.023 --> 00:00:29.175
Zapravo,

00:00:29.175 --> 00:00:34.571
